oracle.dmt.jdm
Class OraMiningAlgorithm

java.lang.Object
  oracle.dmt.jdm.OraMiningAlgorithm

public class OraMiningAlgorithm
extends java.lang.Object

javax.datamining.MiningAlgorithm enumeration lists the JDM standard algorithms as enumerated values. This class declares Oracle data mining algorithm extensions as MiningAlgorithm enumerated values and adds them to the MiningAlgorithm as extension enumerated values.

Field Summary
static javax.datamining.MiningAlgorithm adaptiveBayesNetwork
